							       |         |         |  |        |  |         |         |
							       ---------------------------------  |         -----------
                                                                                      |           |
                                                                                      -------------
	1.user_name -> Table1
	2.city_id -> city_name, country_id, country_name 
	3.country_id -> country_name 
	4.school_id -> school_name


